DATA/RESULTS

Labs:
BMP: Na 144, K 4.8, Cl 108, CO2 19, BUN 42, Cr 1.92 (H), Glu 110, AG 17, Lactate 2.4 (H)
CBC: WBC 19.2 (H), Hgb 10.4 (L), Hct 31.2, Plt 210.
Coags: PT 15.2, INR 1.4.
UA: Yellow, Turbid, LE: Large, Nitrite: Positive, WBC: >100, Bacteria: Many.

